  icon: {fileID: 2800000, guid: 727a75301c3d24613a3ebcec4a24c2c8, type: 3}
  title: Google Cardboard
  sections:
  - heading: About
    text: The Google Cardboard plugin allows you to write code where the user's head
      is tracked by the phone's orientation and the screen is used to render stereoscopic
      images that can combined into an image containing depth using the Google Cardboard
      headset.
    linkText: Quickstart
    url: https://developers.google.com/cardboard/develop/unity/quickstart
  - heading: git Repository
    text: The latest version of the plugin can be found on git hub.
    linkText: 'github '
    url: https://github.com/googlevr/cardboard-xr-plugin
  loadedLayout: 1
